    "tags": [
      "AI / Machine Learning",
      "Developer Tools"
    ],
    "details": "<p>To upgrade the Build Agent application, upgrade the Now Assist for Creator application (sn\\_now\\_creator), which includes the Build Agent Pro plugin (sn\\_build\\_agent\\_pro). To upgrade the Build Agent (Trial) app, upgrade the sn\\_build\\_agent plugin.</p>",
    "link": "https://www.servicenow.com/docs/r/delta-zurich-australia/australia-zurich-nowassistforcreator-release-notes.html",
    "resources": "<a href=\"https://www.servicenow.com/docs/r/application-development/now-assist-for-creator/install-now-assist-for-creator.html\">Install Now Assist for Creator</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.servicenow.com/docs/r/application-development/install-build-agent.html\">Install Build Agent</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.servicenow.com/docs/r/application-development/build-agent.html\">Build Agent in ServiceNow IDE</a>\n<a href=\"https://store.servicenow.com/store/app/779bebaa1b246a50a85b16db234bcbab\">Now Assist for Creator - ServiceNow Store</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.servicenow.com/community/now-assist-for-creator-articles/what-s-new-in-now-assist-for-creator-zurich-release/ta-p/3447117\">What's new in Now Assist for Creator? Zurich Release</a>",
