    "details": "<p><strong><a href=\"https://www.servicenow.com/docs/access?context=rule-based-builder&family=australia&ft:locale=en-US\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Process Step filter (Previously Transition filter) & Rule-based Findings enhanced</a></strong></p>\n<p>Unlock new use cases and drive better process optimization outcomes through the enhanced process step filter and rule-based findings.</p>",
    "link": "https://www.servicenow.com/docs/r/delta-zurich-australia/australia-zurich-processmining-release-notes.html",
    "resources": "<a href=\"https://www.servicenow.com/docs/r/now-intelligence/process-mining/create-transition-manually.html\">Create a process step filter manually</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.servicenow.com/docs/r/now-intelligence/process-mining/analyst-workbench-dashboard.html\">Analyst Workbench</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.servicenow.com/community/process-mining-blog/what-s-new-for-process-mining-in-the-washington-d-c-release/ba-p/2809607\">What's new for Process Mining in the Washington D.C. release</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.servicenow.com/community/process-mining-blog/turn-filters-into-findings-patterns-with-servicenow-process/ba-p/3250699\">Turn Filters into Findings Patterns with ServiceNow Process Mining</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3ccPD9gJi6U\">Process Mining Academy - Turning filter into Finding Definitions</a>",
